&lt;h3 class="relative group"&gt;1. Documentation Preparation
 &lt;div id="1-documentation-preparation" class="anchor"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
 
 &lt;span
 class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none"&gt;
 &lt;a class="text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline" href="#1-documentation-preparation" aria-label="Anchor"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
 &lt;/span&gt;
 
&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To import industrial equipment, you will need to prepare:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contract with the foreign supplier&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Invoice and packing list&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Certificate of origin&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Technical documentation for the equipment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h3 class="relative group"&gt;2. Customs Clearance
 &lt;div id="2-customs-clearance" class="anchor"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
 
 &lt;span
 class="absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none"&gt;
 &lt;a class="text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline" href="#2-customs-clearance" aria-label="Anchor"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
 &lt;/span&gt;
 
&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Customs duties on industrial equipment in Uzbekistan range from 0% to 20% depending on the HS code. Preferential rates are available for certain categories of equipment not manufactured domestically.&lt;/p&gt;</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://nzulkaynarov.github.io/rt-website-public/en/blog/import-customs-guide/featured.jpg"/></item></channel></rss>